---
source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
A plain © sign decodes in running text.

Monospace ``&`` decodes, as do a :sub:`©` subscript, a :sup:`®`
superscript, and a [STRIKEOUT:©] deletion.

A link label `&copy; <start>`__ keeps the entity literal, and so does a
&copy; span and a verbatim block:

::

   &copy;
